speech.p:
asked the Minister of Transport (1) whether the tables he is preparing

showing the progress made in the submission and approval of schemes under the five-year road programme,, will state the several works in the scheme of each highway authority with the estimated cost of the work, the amount or percentage of the Road Fund grant in respect of the same, the date of commencement of the work, and the estimated payment in respect of each grant which will be required during the current financial year;

(2) when he will have ready for circulation the tables which he is preparing showing the progress made in the submission and approval of schemes under the five-year road programme?
